OL,7,FThe Boulton family is one of many to
OL,8,Fspeak to ITV News about significant
OL,9,Fgaps in education provision for
OL,10,Fchildren with additional learning
OL,11,Fneeds, and comes days after a Senedd
OL,12,Fcommittee report found that too many
OL,13,Fchildren with ALN in Wales are being
OL,14,Fdenied their right to an education.
