OL,5,CALN'
OL,7,FAn exclusive poll of parents of
OL,8,Fchildren with ALN found that half of
OL,9,Frespondents in Wales said their child
OL,10,Fhad had to take time out of school
OL,11,Fbecause their needs could not be met.
OL,12,FOf those, 17% said their child had
OL,13,Fbeen out of school for between a month
OL,14,Fand a year.
