OL,3,C'We shouldn't have to fight for an
OL,4,Ceducation for our son because he's got
OL,5,CALN'
OL,7,FMum Chloe told ITV Cymru Wales: "It
OL,8,Fwas probably one of the most
OL,9,Fchallenging times of our lives. It was
OL,10,Fso distressing, we felt in the dark,
OL,11,Ffelt like you were fighting for
OL,12,Fsomething that should have be a given
OL,13,Fright to your child: the right to an
OL,14,Feducation.
OL,16,F"Just because he's got additional
OL,17,Flearning needs, he shouldn't have to
OL,18,Ffight.
