OL,3,C'We shouldn't have to fight for an
OL,4,Ceducation for our son because he's got
OL,5,CALN'
OL,7,F"That was a separate challenge, trying
OL,8,Fto get him to be seen in the
OL,9,Fneurodevelopmental team took so long.
OL,10,FHis name went to them in December 2021
OL,11,Fand he was diagnosed a couple of
OL,12,Fmonths ago."
OL,14,FBoth parents are calling for more
OL,15,Fsupport for parents to navigate their
OL,16,Fway to accessing suitable support.
OL,18,FDad Craig said: "It was a minefield,
OL,19,Freally. It was like being in a maze at
OL,20,Fnight.
