OL,3,C'We shouldn't have to fight for an
OL,4,Ceducation for our son because he's got
OL,5,CALN'
OL,7,F"The whole process is so difficult to
OL,8,Fget through. I think the local
OL,9,Fauthority could do more to illuminate
OL,10,Fthat maze and help you to get through
OL,11,Fit a bit easier. It is an emotional
OL,12,Frollercoaster anyway, plus it's a very
OL,13,Fdifficult system: deadlines, evidence
OL,14,Fneeded.
OL,16,F"It's very difficult when you've got
OL,17,Ftwo full-time jobs and a family. It's
OL,18,Fa grind.
