OL,3,C'We shouldn't have to fight for an
OL,4,Ceducation for our son because he's got
OL,5,CALN'
OL,7,F"However, where a specialist placement
OL,8,Fis required, there are no waiting
OL,9,Flists for these in Rhondda Cynon Taf.
OL,11,F"We have processes in place in line
OL,12,FALN legislation to ensure that a
OL,13,Flearner's needs are fully identified
OL,14,Fand appropriate support is put in
OL,15,Fplace in a timely manner. Specialist
OL,16,Fplacements are made available to
OL,17,Fpupils as necessary and in line with
OL,18,Ftheir identified ALN."
